## Fragile Zones (Last 30 Days)
<!-- Tags on incomplete sessions — recent window only -->
```dataview
TABLE length(rows) AS "Incomplete", round(sum(rows.cost_usd), 2) AS "Cost Burned"
FROM ".claude-code-hermit/sessions"
WHERE id AND (status = "blocked" OR status = "partial") AND date >= date(today) - dur(30 days)
FLATTEN tags AS tag
GROUP BY tag
SORT length(rows) DESC
LIMIT 5
```

## What Just Changed
```dataview
TABLE date, task, status, cost_usd AS "Cost"
FROM ".claude-code-hermit/sessions"
WHERE id
SORT date DESC
LIMIT 5
```

## Needs Attention
<!-- Accepted proposals waiting for implementation -->
```dataview
TABLE title, category, accepted_date
FROM ".claude-code-hermit/proposals"
WHERE id AND status = "accepted"
SORT accepted_date ASC
```

